Package.resolved

# Multi-service apps built from this repo root (RemoteCamViewer, MeshBeacon,
# MeshCounter, ...) each keep a canonical Dockerfile.<appname> checked in;
# deploying one copies it to the bare `Dockerfile` wendy CLI's build step
# expects, so that transient copy must never itself be committed.
/Dockerfile
